lead_paragraph: Philadelphia, which sent Jonathan Papelbon to Washington on Tuesday, will acquire five prospects and the left-hander Matt Harrison, according to an official with knowledge of the talks.

headline.main: Phillies Said to Be Trading Cole Hamels to Rangers
